<Base title="About Us - The Little Graduates" description="A warm, joyful Montessori preschool in the heart of Kaloor, Kochi — for children aged 1.5 to 6.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="kicker center">About us</p>
      <h1 class="center">A warm start. A joyful future.</h1>
      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;">A warm, joyful preschool in the heart of Kaloor, Kochi — for children aged 1.5 to 6. We believe the early years shape everything that comes next. Our 6T Curriculum blends Montessori principles, play-based learning, and hands-on skill building — so every child grows in confidence, curiosity, and kindness.</p>
      <p>With experienced teachers, modern facilities, and a strong focus on emotional and social development, your child won't just learn here. They'll feel at home.</p>

      <h2>Beyond Montessori — children learn by doing</h2>
      <p>We go beyond traditional Montessori with daily hands-on sessions, STEM, art, storytelling, and real-world exploration. With 600+ Montessori materials, dedicated Montessori hours, and child-led play, every day builds a confident, lifelong learner.</p>

      <h2>How we teach</h2>
      <h3>Image of the child</h3>
      <p>Teachers build on what children already know — by closely observing their interests, having meaningful one-on-one conversations, and gently inviting them to explore deeper.</p>
      <h3>Positive discipline</h3>
      <p>Discipline comes from guidance, not punishment. We don't allow corporal punishment of any kind. Instead, we help children understand boundaries with empathy, respect, and gentle redirection.</p>
      <h3>Environment matters</h3>
      <p>A thoughtfully prepared space — calm, beautiful, accessible — encourages independence, focus, and exploration. When the space is respectful and nurturing, children thrive.</p>

      <h2>Meet Remya — Centre Head &amp; Founder</h2>
      <blockquote>"After 12 years as a Senior Project Manager in IT, I followed my passion for early childhood education — to create a nurturing space in Kochi where children learn through love, play, and curiosity."</blockquote>

      <div class="banner" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <div><h2>Come see for yourself</h2><p>Free 30-minute campus tour — any day that works for you.</p></div>
        <a class="btn btn-white" href="/book-a-tour/">Book a tour →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
